OL,3,CLondon Underground services return to
OL,4,Cnormal after strike by drivers
OL,6,FLondon Underground services returned
OL,7,Fto normal on Wednesday after a strike
OL,8,Fby drivers which caused huge
OL,9,Fdisruption to travellers.
OL,11,FMembers of the Rail, Maritime and
OL,12,FTransport union (RMT) walked out on
OL,13,FTuesday and will strike again on
OL,14,FThursday in a dispute over a four-day
OL,15,Fweek.
OL,17,FThe union says it expects fresh talks
OL,18,Fto be held next week in a bid to
OL,19,Fresolve the row.
