FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1780589464
OL,3,CLondon Underground services return to
OL,4,Cnormal after strike by drivers
OL,6,FClive Wood, of Guide Dogs, said the
OL,7,Fstrikes created additional challenges
OL,8,Ffor people with a vision impairment,
OL,9,Fas changes to usual routes and travel
OL,10,Fpatterns make getting around more
OL,11,Fdifficult.
OL,13,FHr said: "Tube closures can lead to
OL,14,Fincreased traffic, busier pavements,
OL,15,Fand more crowded public spaces and
OL,16,Fbuses."
OL,18,FHe said many e-bikes and scooters were
OL,19,Fpoorly parked and blocked pavements,
OL,20,Fposing risks for pedestrians with
OL,21,Fsight loss.
OL,26,@uD@JOUxD@GO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/5
