OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,408,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F407A1780589464
OL,3,CLondon Underground services return to
OL,4,Cnormal after strike by drivers
OL,6,F"For some, these factors may make
OL,7,Fjourneys feel unpredictable or unsafe,
OL,8,Fand may lead them to avoid travelling
OL,9,Faltogether, limiting their
OL,10,Findependence," he added.
OL,12,F"We're asking commuters to remember
OL,13,Fthat while trains may stop, the need
OL,14,Ffor accessibility doesn't. A small act
OL,15,Flike moving a hire bike or giving up a
OL,16,Fspace or a seat can be the difference
OL,17,Fbetween a safe journey and a dangerous
OL,18,Fone for a person with sight loss."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@NO]tD@AOUzD@bO]
